{"tid":339544,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陰公，蒸魚安想串堂主，點知連雲粉都當佢狗咁撚","createTime":"2017-07-29T07:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T17:28:03.000Z","uid":30807,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2e87c1f38cdeedbdb3d72f097bc9060e813845","tid":339544,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T07:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8k5rvnes\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8k5rvnes&h=5085382c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話哂都叫讀過下書，為左痴熱狗，早前埋沒良心仲堅稱書展一役係殘獸胃智破仇思達<br />\n<br />\n蒸魚安衰衰地都叫寫左本香港文化論，只論學識一定叻過99%熱血城邦信徒，可惜無人賞識，更一度淪為清算對象。<br />\n<br />\n如今已變成熱血城邦及本土派共同恥笑的「不是人」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8qbw90o5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8qbw90o5&h=4ed27881&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1ify36b2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1ify36b2&h=5eee847d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒸魚安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ty8p9uxh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fty8p9uxh&h=d8dc769e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ma0yp86k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fma0yp86k&h=0aaa9421&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"733795d9306b4d0f28591db5fb5c624ee48b3593","tid":339544,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:08:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/8k5rvnes\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8k5rvnes&h=5085382c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話哂都叫讀過下書，為左痴熱狗，早前埋沒良心仲堅稱書展一役係殘獸胃智破仇思達<br />\n<br />\n蒸魚安衰衰地都叫寫左本香港文化論，只論學識一定叻過99%熱血城邦信徒，可惜無人賞識，更一度淪為清算對象。<br />\n<br />\n如今已變成熱血城邦及本土派共同恥笑的「不是人」<br />\n